Here we publish the source MATLAB files of the anisotropic FDTD algorithm. All rights reserved.

Run MASTER.m to set the model and simulation parameters, and to run the simulation.

Run SAVE.m to write saved data to .GIF or INDEXED MATLAB files. 

Run PLOT_inx.m to visualize saved INDEXED MATLAB files.

Referred article: Okada, Naoki, and James B. Cole. "FDTD modeling of a cloak with a nondiagonal permittivity tensor." ISRN Optics 2012 (2012).
